=====
caprun when edit.

Every time you edit React code, you must run these in order:
cd ~/Desktop/solride/frontend
# 1. Compile React → static bundle
yarn build
# 2. Copy the new bundle into the iOS app
npx cap sync ios
# 3. In Xcode: Stop the running sim (red square) → Hit Play
echo 'alias caprun="cd ~/Desktop/solride/frontend && yarn build && npx cap sync ios"' >> ~/.zshrc
source ~/.zshrc
Then every time you save changes, just type:
caprun

